PURPOSE:-
--------
Test local repair.



SCENARIO:-
---------

--------- means a normal link.
----X---- means a broken link

1-----2--X--3-----4-----5
      \          /
       \        /
        6------7


Node1 sends a packet to Node 4 before the link break and another one after
the link break.  The second packet does not reach at Node 4 because the
repaired path is longer than original.



RUN:-
----
Run '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet default.config'.


DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. default.app -  QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. default.config - QualNet configuration input file.
3. default.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
4. default.fault - QualNet configuration file for fault.
5. default.nodes - QualNet node position file.
6. README - This file.
